::DarkMouse::

She looked at Destructor,"What's wrong?" She found herself actually 
wondering about him.  She shook her head.  No bot in his right mind 
would gave a care in the pit about her.  She turned and walked a few 
feet away.  She looked at the growing amount of Maximals. She felt 
the urge to run, but stood there, hoping that she wouldn't get 
slagged.
